0.0.4.0
   Features:
        - Added many unit test
        - Initial support for --vm option to autobuild virtual machine for testing
   Bug fixes:
        Users can now install anouman packages in other directorie.

0.0.5.0
    Updates:
        -Refactored the template code to be more extinsible
        -Changed naming scheme of nginx conf from "nginx.domainname.conf" to "domainname"
        

    Features:
        -Better support for multisite installs 
        -Finished --vm option for auto creation of virtual machines
